    "customize": [
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 2,
        "text": "玩法教學"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "<color=#ffffff>玩法教學1</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/57df4b1a1250c7ef855496edd3382c43_9081237747484936617.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "旅行者需要裝備「留影機」，與留影點互動後進入留影模式。留影分為留影設定調整階段，和可以移動以及施放技能的留影階段。\n<color=#ffffff>玩法教學2</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/20170a14809f5514d3edac35a35deaee_295159628689041956.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "在留影點調整階段，旅行者首先需要選擇一個留影設定，並可以在此設定的基礎上繼續調整留影的位置和角度。\n需要注意的是， <color=#ffe14b>留影點</color> 需要在留影範圍內。確認留影設定後，進入留影階段。\n<color=#ffffff>玩法教學3</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/2837e78705ce084aae0c55ed1046ccfc_2407733174847835579.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "在留影階段，當旅行者使用「留影機」拍攝畫片時，畫片完成時的角度將由之前所調整的留影設定決定。\n在留影過程中，留影的方向會由「留影射光」指示。\n<color=#ffffff>玩法教學4</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/16/125391187/d81abd172edd9b8c69e12e7bef909cd3_1865695868843647055.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "若想重新調整留影設定，也可以點擊終端挑戰，選擇回到預設重新調整留影設定。\n完成留影後，若想繼續使用目前的留影設定繼續留影，可以點擊繼續留影回到留影階段。\n<color=#ffffff>玩法教學5</color>",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/31/125391187/5d7775f835de3f914717de62227fb320_8388926527176302389.png",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "當實現拍攝目標時即可獲得獎勵。如果同時實現所有目標，活動螢幕上會出現一個額外的標記。",
        "alignment": "center"
      }
    ]
  }
}